<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Prayer area<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">On-site chapel<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent29471f19098941fdbfae27c7db73207a">
</div>
<p>The Faith and Community Centre is located on Level 1 of the hospital, near the Main Entrance. The centre offers the following facilities:</p>
<ul>
<li>Chapel</li>
<li>Prayer Rooms</li>
<li>Wudu' rooms</li>
<li>Quiet corner (open 24/7)</li>
<li>Meeting rooms</li>
<li>Chaplaincy offices</li>
</ul>
<p>Everyone is welcome to use our facilities.</p>
<p>Members of the Chaplaincy Team also visit patients in wards and departments, providing spiritual care as requested by patients and families.</p>
</div>
